STATE of Louisiana
v.
Bennie TEMPLE No. 2018-KK-626 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 27, 2018 ON SUPERVISORY WRIT TO THE CRIMINAL DISTRICT COURT, PARISH OF ORLEANS Writ denied. GENOVESE, J., additionally concurs and assigns reasons. GENOVESE, J., additionally concurs in the denial of the writ.
